body.p:
Add the XML domain to the domains attribute declaration. In concept.dtd,
			find the comment that says "DOMAINS ATTRIBUTE OVERRIDE". Update the
				included-domains entity declaration to include the
				xml-d-att text entity:
			
<!ENTITY included-domains 
   "&hi-d-att; 
    &ut-d-att; 
    &xml-d-att; 
   "                
>
